{"tid":1389079,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【大家入嚟諗諗】精神病患者能否擔任警隊前線(配槍)職務？","createTime":"2019-07-30T21:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:55:26.000Z","uid":260381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8e3d814aa1db2421f5b154e9e9427255c8ab15","tid":1389079,"uid":260381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:34:37.000Z","msg":"2016年有單新聞【法庭在審判一宗警員用氣槍傷害猴子的案件，當裁判官得知被告在過去兩年一直有向精神科求診時，問了一句「有精神病仲可做警察？」似是質疑被告因為患有精神病，而不應繼續履行警察職務。】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無得循法律途徑，去禁制疑似精神病患者履行警察職務？</span></span>"},{"pid":"37443829827b3524bf9b8c1eadf01e4f491bb311","tid":1389079,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:35:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2772c4d6702f05d7f87e1ba47674714cc9906829","tid":1389079,"uid":260381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37443829827b3524bf9b8c1eadf01e4f491bb311","tid":1389079,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:35:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:37:12.000Z","msg":"我查過警察條例及立法局會議紀錄，原來有精神病係可以繼續做警察。無一條例話唔得"},{"pid":"05363f9322d2a9d83cfb9f8d1593855765b0ed03","tid":1389079,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:38:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c99891c6110296834d094ebc8378cd0dcc6bd45","tid":1389079,"uid":260381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:42:07.000Z","msg":"可以參考返哩份文件：【臨時立法會保安事務委員會<br />\n特別會議紀要 ：警方對待精神有問題的警務人員及處理相關事宜的政策】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr97-98/chinese/panels/se/minutes/se171197.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr97-98%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fminutes%2Fse171197.htm&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij85qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=d438a278\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr97-98/chinese/panels/se/minutes/se171197.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f890940ecb594766ae17ef6b15149fd031b5